          The interplay between sales taxes and property taxes in {name} is particularly important for homeowners, who must budget for both recurring obligations. With a median annual property tax of {formatCurrencyRound(propTax.medianAnnualTax)} and a sales tax that adds {formatPercent(salesTax.avgCombinedRate * 100)} to most purchases, the combined effect on a household's finances can be substantial. Homeowners in {name} should consider both of these costs when evaluating the total affordability of living in a particular community, as property tax rates can vary significantly between counties and municipalities, just as combined sales tax rates can vary between cities.
        </p>
